SKILL.md was rewritten to push richer behavior out of the core CLI and into workflow recipes.

Key shifts:
- On arrival, agents are pointed at `scripts/context-workflow.sh`.
- Historical file notes are taught via `scripts/path-history.sh`.
- Overwrite history is taught via `scripts/note-history.sh` and raw git log on the notes ref.
- `compost` remains available but is no longer framed as the default path.

This is the main dogfooding change for the repo itself.
